| Function               | Purpose                          |
| ---------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| `pd.Series()`          | Create a single column (1D data) |
| `pd.DataFrame()`       | Create a table (2D data)         |
| `df.loc[]`             | Select by label                  |
| `df.iloc[]`            | Select by index number           |
| `df.drop()`            | Remove rows/columns              |
| `df.rename()`          | Rename columns or rows           |
| `df.dropna()`          | Remove missing values            |
| `df.fillna()`          | Fill missing values              |
| `df.drop_duplicates()` | Remove duplicate rows            |
| `df.apply()`           | Apply function to data           |
| `pd.merge()`           | Combine DataFrames               |
| `pd.read_csv()`        | Read data from CSV file          |
| `pd.read_excel()`      | Read data from Excel file        |
| `pd.read_json()`       | Read data from JSON format       |
| `pd.to_datetime()`     | Convert to date/time type        |
| `df.astype()`          | Change data type                 |
